name: BMO U.S. Equity Growth MFR Fund
longDescription: The fund investing primarily in equity securities of U.S. companies that offer above average prospects for growth. The Fund follows a disciplined multi-factor security analysis to identify growth-oriented companies based on fundamental ratios and trading statistics. This funds objective is to provide longterm capital growth.
